divs: Sighting DetailsI was out on my friends patio on Chautauqua Lake. I was cleaning up his grill when i saw a giant Gold circle in the sky. It stayed in the same place for about 30-45 sec. shining a very bright gold. I went to get my friend and by the time we got back outside it was gone.
